Musa Keys:
Musa Keys have 5 songs on the Spotify Top 200 Weekly South Africa chart. 
 They first appeared on the chart on 2020-12-03. Their most recent appearance has been on 2023-11-16. They have a total of 6297115 million streams. 
. His highest position on the chart is 4 for the song Vula Mlomo which was at this position on 2021-04-01
 The songs of his that have appeared on the chart are Izinyembezi ... Samarian Boy ... Selema (Po Po) ... Thando Lwami ... Vula Mlomo
